===Noun===
'''falsetto'''
{{wikipedia}}
#(countable or uncountable) The highest ([[singing]]) [[voice]] in any [[male]] [[human]], usually clear and in the female [[alto]] and [[soprano]] ranges; created by utilizing the next highest [[vocal]] [[folds]] above those used for speech and normal [[range]] singing.
